sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant AI as AI Platform
    participant ContextHook as arckit-context.sh Hook
    participant ReviewCmd as /arckit.hld-review or /arckit.dld-review
    participant VendorDoc as Vendor HLD/DLD Document
    
    User->>AI: /arckit.hld-review Review Acme Corp HLD
    AI->>ContextHook: UserPromptSubmit event
    ContextHook->>ContextHook: Scan projects/*/vendors/*/
    ContextHook->>ContextHook: Scan projects/*/external/
    ContextHook->>ContextHook: Scan projects/000-global/external/
    ContextHook-->>AI: Inject vendor document paths via systemMessage
    AI->>ReviewCmd: Execute with vendor doc context
    ReviewCmd->>VendorDoc: Read vendor-hld.pdf or hld-v1.md
    VendorDoc-->>ReviewCmd: Extract architecture diagrams, API specs, security controls
    ReviewCmd->>ReviewCmd: Generate review with "External References" table
    ReviewCmd-->>User: Write ARC-{PID}-HLDR-v1.0.md
